---
import ImageCarousel from "../components/ImageCarousel.astro";
import ImageGallery from "../components/ImageGallery.astro";
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout>
  <h2 class="pt-4 pt-sm-5 h2">Annual Meeting</h2>Held in town each summer. Check
  the
  <a href="/documents" target="_blank">newsletter</a> for details!

  <h2 class="pt-4 pt-sm-5 h2">2024 Annual Homeowner Cleanup</h2>We added more bins this year with support 
  from Firewise and the North Tahoe Fire District. Thanks to everyone who helped keep our neighborhood safe!
  <div class="pt-2">
    <ImageGallery
      images={[
        { src: "/img/events/2024_cleanup/1.jpg" },
        { src: "/img/events/2024_cleanup/2.jpg" },
      ]}
    />
  </div>

  <h2 class="pt-4 pt-sm-5 h2">2023 Greenbelt Cleanup</h2>This summer we have been
  busy taking out dead and dying trees in 2 of our 4 greenbelts to help with
  fire protection, we hope all residents can help with defensible space on their
  properties, we are working on getting bins for pine needle cleanup again in
  the spring.
  <div class="pt-2">
    <ImageGallery
      images={[
        { src: "/img/events/2023_greenbelts/0815.jpg" },
        { src: "/img/events/2023_greenbelts/0816.jpg" },
      ]}
    />
  </div>

  <h2 class="pt-4 pt-sm-5 h2">2023 Annual Homeowner Cleanup</h2>Neighbors helped
  neighbors clean our community and prevent the spread of wildfire. Thanks to
  all that took part in this important event!
  <div class="pt-2">
    <ImageGallery
      images={[
        { src: "/img/events/2023_cleanup/5525.jpg" },
        { src: "/img/events/2023_cleanup/5521.jpg" },
        { src: "/img/events/2023_cleanup/5519.jpg" },
      ]}
    />
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
